---
title: Indian-Style Ground Tofu Curry with Sweet Potato and Basmati Rice
description: Tofu curry is quick, simple and packed with bold, Indian-inspired flavours! This creamy curry also gets a silky boost from coconut milk, bringing a hint of luxury to your weeknight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/indian-style-ground-tofu-curry-71548646.jpg
